ygData.messageBody:
Ok I wanted to see what my AoE song's damages were tonite so I dueled a friend of mine. I had seen other people document what their's did so I was going to see for myself. Well we did the typical /duel to each other and my songs had no effect. No messages or anything. They just made the pretty lights when I first started them and then nothing. I did a bellow and he took damage. What am I missing? He is a level 28 by the way, but I dont see what the level difference would have to do with it, besides him kicking my butt. 8)

Kurik Nitesong
21st bard
Veeshan
